	<h1 class="title">这个世界好污：政客们为了自己的钱都做了什么</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43810/small/43810.jpg?1421878384" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">The Associated Press</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-04 15:46:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/24913/medium/24913.jpg?1459753962" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


